    <title>数学笔记--微积分(1)</title>
    <link href="/2020/08/01/learn-math-1/"/>
    <url>/2020/08/01/learn-math-1/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script type="text/javascript"   src="http://cdn.mathjax.org/mathjax/latest/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_HTMLorMML"></script><h1 id="函数笔记"><a href="#函数笔记" class="headerlink" title="函数笔记"></a>函数笔记</h1><h2 id="1-三角函数"><a href="#1-三角函数" class="headerlink" title="1. 三角函数"></a>1. 三角函数</h2><p>$$sin(A+B)=cos(A) \times sin(B)+sin(A) \times cos(B)$$<br>$$cos(A-B)=cos(A) \times cos(B)-sin(A) \times sin(B)$$<br>证明: 由欧拉定理\(e^{ix}=cos(x)+i \times sin(x)\) (泰勒级数展开可得)<br>\(\qquad e^{iA+iB}\)<br>\(=cos(A+B)+i \times sin(A+B)\)<br>\(=e^{iA} \times e^{iB}\)<br>\(=(cos(A)+i \times sin(A)) \times (cos(B)+i \times sin(B))\)<br>\(=cos(A) \times cos(B)-sin(A) \times sin(B)+i \times (sin(A) \times cos(B)+cos(A) \times sin(B))\)<br>得证</p><h2 id="2-连续性"><a href="#2-连续性" class="headerlink" title="2. 连续性"></a>2. 连续性</h2><p>$$lim_{x-&gt;a^-}f(x)=lim_{x-&gt;a^+}f(x)=f(a)$$</p><h2 id="3-中值定理"><a href="#3-中值定理" class="headerlink" title="3. 中值定理"></a>3. 中值定理</h2><p>$$f(x)在[a,b]上连续，若f(a)&lt;0,f(b)&gt;=0,则存在f(c)=0,a&lt;c&lt;b$$</p>]]></content>
    
    
